status: Доктор Фрост (Serbian); 닥터 프로스트 (Korean); الدكتور فروست (Arabic); 神探佛斯特 (Chinese); 닥터 프로스트 (Korean); Tiến Sĩ Frost (Vietnames - Tiếng Việt - TV)
description:
Description :
        We trust professionals with our money. We also trust professionals with our bodies. We even trust them with the most meticulous tasks, like decorating our homes and educating our children. Even marriage decisions. We could trust professionals with so many things. However, what about our minds? The story of a genius psychologist, Dr. Frost.
